OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1777986670
OL,3,CUrgent action taken to remove trees
OL,4,Cinfected with Ash Dieback from woodland
OL,6,FUrgent action is being taken to remove
OL,7,Ftrees infected with Ash Dieback from a
OL,8,Fwoodland near Waterlooville.
OL,10,FHavant Borough Council said the
OL,11,Faffected area of Hurstwood will be
OL,12,Ffenced off and visitors will not be
OL,13,Fable to enter until the work is
OL,14,Fcomplete.
OL,16,FAsh Dieback is a serious fungal
OL,17,Fdisease which is threatening up to 80%
OL,18,Fof the UK's ash trees.
OL,20,FThe fungus weakens the trees and kills
OL,21,Fthem.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
