PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1777986670
OL,3,CUrgent action taken to remove trees
OL,4,Cinfected with Ash Dieback from woodland
OL,6,FMatt Goodwin, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FHavant Borough Council said: "It's
OL,8,Fdevastating to see local woodlands,
OL,9,Flike trees in so many parts of the UK,
OL,10,Fbeing decimated by ash dieback.
OL,12,F"The branches of affected trees
OL,13,Fquickly become brittle, and the
OL,14,Fbranches ` and in some cases the
OL,15,Fentire tree ` can fall with very
OL,16,Flittle warning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
