PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1777986670
OL,3,CUrgent action taken to remove trees
OL,4,Cinfected with Ash Dieback from woodland
OL,6,FMatt Goodwin, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FHavant Borough Council , says, "We are
OL,8,Fabsolutely committed to only removing
OL,9,Ftrees when necessary and making sure
OL,10,Fthat we do this in the most
OL,11,Fecologically friendly way possible and
OL,12,Fby managing these trees in this
OL,13,Fresponsible way, we will be creating
OL,14,Fnew opportunities for plant and
OL,15,Fwildlife regeneration."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
